hi guys,
xgboost export is now available (and exposed) in Onnxmltools repo - https://github.com/onnx/onnxmltools/pull/318

I am aware that xgboost has a RFC for a new export format, however given that onnx is supporting xgboost - will the xgboost project considering adopting ONNX as *one* of the officially supported export formats ?
